headline: Fluor's Stock Soars 55% in 3 Months: Should You Buy the Surge or Wait?
summary: FLR shares surge 55% in three months on rising backlog and buybacks - but should new investors wait for a better entry?

headline: CMC Announces Appointment of Dawne S. Hickton to Board of Directors
summary: Commercial Metals Company (NYSE: CMC) ("CMC" or the "Company") today announced that it has named Dawne S. Hickton to the Company's Board of Directors (the "Board"), effective October 14, 2025.
